Package: paleopop
Type: Package
Title: Pattern-oriented Modelling Framework for Coupled Niche-population Paleo-climatic Models
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sean", "Haythorne", email = "sean.haythorne@adelaide.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Julia", "Pilowsky", email = "julia.pilowsky@adelaide.edu.au", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Sean Haythorne <sean.haythorne@adelaide.edu.au>
Description: This extension of the poems pattern-oriented modelling (POM) framework 
    provides a collection of modules and functions customized for paleontological 
    time-scales, and optimized for single-generation transitions and large populations, 
    across multiple generations.
